      <title>埃尔德里奇（Eldridge）的臂贷款2亿英镑用于英国学生住房</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/eldridge-credit-arm-lends-200-million-for-uk-student-housing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[学生住房提供商Vita Group Holdings Ltd.已从Eldridge Capital Management的房地产信贷部门获得了超过2亿英镑（2.54亿美元）的债务融资，以在伦敦的金丝雀码头附近建造一座48层的塔楼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/eldridge-credit-arm-lends-200-million-for-uk-student-housing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
